{"type":"text","timestamp":1775849441321,"sessionID":"ses_287215b25ffe7CZXXnfStOQX5W","part":{"id":"prt_d78e0029a001EvS622UWI5OUKs","messageID":"msg_d78dfedc2001T9nY3f4xf2euaw","sessionID":"ses_287215b25ffe7CZXXnfStOQX5W","type":"text","text":"Done. The delta-spec.md has been updated with additional scenarios for:\n\n1. **Audience validation** - Validate aud claim, reject wrong audience\n2. **Clock skew handling** - Accept tokens expiring within tolerance window  \n3. **JWT Metrics** - Track validation success/failure and token issuance\n\nThe spec now covers all acceptance criteria from the proposal including metrics, audience validation, and clock skew handling. Total: 272 lines with comprehensive GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios.","time":{"start":1775849441320,"end":1775849441320}}}
